caption.title: Comparison between the accepted simulations by ABC and the data from the 2010–2011 season to the 2014–2015 season.
caption.p: Each gray line shows the accepted simulation run by ABC. The dashed line shows the average of the accepted simulation runs by ABC. The black line shows the data of the weekly reported number of isolates. The top panel shows the isolation of Victoria lineage and the bottom panel shows the isolation of Yamagata.
